episodes.description:
Unacademy presents Operation MBBS

Huma, Nishant and Sakshi gear up for their final exams. As Huma considers whether to cheat or not, the others learn something about her which irreversibly changes her image. 
Meanwhile, Nishant is hell bent on not studying, having renounced the field of medicine after what happened to his father. 
Both of their plans change when faced with an immediate challenge.

episodes.title: Dice Media | Operation MBBS | Web Series | Episode 3 - Complications ft. Ayush Mehra
episodes.description:
Unacademy presents Operation MBBS

Do exams define who you are? Find out in Episode 3!
Mid term results are in for our students and they're in for a surprise. As they celebrate their results, they realize that there's something much deeper at play which they need to address.

episodes.title: Dice Media | Operation MBBS | Web Series | Episode 1 - Infection ft. Ayush Mehra
episodes.description:
Unacademy presents Operation MBBS  

Will Nishant, Sakshi and Huma make it through the first week of college? Let's find out!

We follow Nishant, Sakshi and Huma, fresh, first year MBBS students, as they go through the first few weeks of college and meet all kinds of quirky and unique people. An incident in the dissection hall ends with Nishant figuring out how to apologise to the two girls.

episodes.title: Dice Media | Operation MBBS | Web Series | Episode 2 - Diagnosis ft. Ayush Mehra
episodes.description:
Unacademy presents Operation MBBS

Sakshi and Huma learn something about Nishant which changes their perception of him!

A month into the first year of MBBS, Nishant, Huma and Sakshi balance an infinite syllabus, difficult practicals and the desire to actually enjoy their college life. But as their party comes to an abrupt end, they learn something about Nishant which changes their perception of him.

episodes.description:
Unacademy presents Operation MBBS

After the big fight, will Nishant, Huma and Sakshi get back together?
Find out in Episode 4!
As Huma struggles to gain back the confidence she's lost, Rukmini gives her a tricky solution. Meanwhile, as the three hold on to their resentments against each other, a heartbreaking event forces them to reconsider what it is that really matters to them.
